---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - OurCouple" description="Privacy Policy for OurCouple app">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 glass">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="OurCouple" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl" />
        <span class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-text">OurCouple</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-1 pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">Last updated: January 21, 2026</p>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and website.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            This policy applies to our landing page (waitlist), our mobile application, and all related services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text mb-3 mt-6">Waitlist (Landing Page)</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">When you sign up for our waitlist, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Your email address</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text mb-3 mt-6">Mobile Application</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">When you use our app, we collect:</p>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text mb-3 mt-6">Automatically Collected</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Device type and operating system (for compatibility)</li>
            <li>App version</li>
            <li>Error logs (anonymized, via Sentry)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">If you are in the European Economic Area (EEA), we process your data based on:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Contract:</strong> to provide you with our services</li>
            <li><strong>Consent:</strong> for marketing communications (waitlist)</li>
            <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> to improve our services and fix bugs</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the app</li>
            <li>Sync your data between your devices</li>
            <li>Share your content with your connected partner only</li>
            <li>Send push notifications for events, reminders, and daily manifestations (with your permission)</li>
            <li>Notify you about product updates and launch (waitlist subscribers)</li>
            <li>Respond to support requests</li>
            <li>Detect and fix bugs (anonymized error tracking)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Partner Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple is designed for couples. When you connect with a partner, certain content is shared with them:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Daily Manifestation messages and photos</li>
            <li>Inspiration Vault quotes (randomly displayed)</li>
            <li>Shared Moments and Shared Notes</li>
            <li>Events & Dates</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            By inviting a partner or accepting an invitation, you consent to sharing this content with them. You can disconnect from your partner at any time in the app settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Data Storage & Security</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Your data is stored securely using Supabase, with encryption at rest (AES-256) and in transit (TLS 1.3). We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Your content is private and only accessible to you and your connected partner. <strong>We do not access, read, or analyze your personal content.</strong> We do not share, sell, or use your content for advertising or any purpose other than providing our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">We use the following third-party services to operate our app:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Supabase</strong> (EU/US) - Database, authentication, and file storage</li>
            <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong> (US) - Subscription and payment management</li>
            <li><strong>Sentry</strong> (US) - Error tracking (anonymized, no personal content)</li>
            <li><strong>Expo</strong> (US) - Push notification delivery</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            Each service has its own privacy policy. We only share the minimum data necessary for each service to function.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">International Data Transfers</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Your data may be transferred to and processed in countries outside your country of residence, including the United States. These countries may have different data protection laws. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place, including standard contractual clauses approved by the European Commission where applicable.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> request a copy of your personal data</li>
            <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
            <li><strong>Portability:</strong> export your data in a machine-readable format</li>
            <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> limit how we process your data</li>
            <li><strong>Objection:</strong> object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
            <li><strong>Withdraw consent:</strong> unsubscribe from waitlist emails at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">contact@vynse.dev</a>. We will respond within 30 days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Active accounts:</strong> data is retained as long as your account is active</li>
            <li><strong>Deleted accounts:</strong> all data is permanently deleted within 30 days</li>
            <li><strong>Waitlist:</strong> email is retained until you unsubscribe or the app launches</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple is not intended for children under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 16. If you believe we have collected data from a child, please contact us immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the new policy on this page, updating the "Last updated" date, and sending a notification through the app or email for significant changes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium">
            <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev">contact@vynse.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors font-medium">
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-card border-t border-border py-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-text-light text-sm">
        ¬© 2026 OurCouple. Made with üíï
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
